text:
"Hey Cipher, you hear me? Just look at the view. There's not much difference between those countires from up here." - Pixy

I woun't spoil it for anyone who's yet to play AC-zero, but he does have a point, Granted some parts of the world may not look entirely alike, yet in the end be it Strangereal or Earth, it's all terra-firma. It's games like this (including argubly Call of duty, Syphon Filter, Metal Gear and Splinter cell to name a few) that makes you think about war on more than one level.

text:
McDonnell-Douglas F-15C, the standard air to air fighter of the United States Air Force, till the F/A-22 Raptor comes online fully.

The greatest thing about the F-15 is its amazing survivability.

An Israel Defense Force F-15 once came back with only one wing, literally, which stunned even the manufactors as they didn't even think that the F-15 could do that.

That is how Pixie became known as Solo Wing Pixie, or at least the more popular myth.
